title: STRAIGHT FROM THE TOUR BUS: Roni Shanell — One Night Only
comedians: STRAIGHT FROM THE TOUR BUS: Roni Shanell — One Night Only
description:
Fresh off Martin Lawrence's sold-out "Y'all Know What It Is" national tour, Detroit's Roni Shanell takes the stage for one night only at the Black Women in Comedy Laff Fest. She's headlined Carolines on Broadway, won Sway in the Morning's Comedy Search, and tours the world performing for U.S. troops — but Friday night, she's here. Sharp, raw, and unapologetically funny. This is the set people talk about the next morning. One mic. One night. Don't be the person who hears about it later.

Featuring:
Lulu Jackson
Ashima Franklin
Sonia Denis
Monique Latise
Storhm Artiste
